Timothy Carey https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Timothy_Carey 0 Timothy Agoglia Carey (March 11, 1929 – May 11, 1994) was an American film and television character actor. Carey was best known for portraying manic or violent characters who are driven to extremes.
